lead_paragraph: Jack Eichel scored two goals in the third period, and the Buffalo Sabres beat the New York Rangers 4-3 on Thursday night for their second straight victory.

headline.print_headline: Eichel's 2 Goals Lead Sabres to 4-3 Win Over Rangers
